Introduction

Ahnatchaya Suputhipong, known under her stage name Natty, is a Thai dancer, singer-songwriter, composer, and choreographer under S2 Entertainment. Formerly under JYP Entertainment and Swing Entertainment. She is best known as the main dancer of the girl group KISS OF LIFE.

In 2015, she became a contestant on JYP's reality survival show SIXTEEN, the survival show that created the girl group TWICE, but was eliminated in episode 11 and hence did not debut.

On April 6, 2020, it was announced that she had signed a contract with Swing Entertainment. She made her solo debut on May 7, 2020 with the single album "NineTeen".

On May 15, 2023, Natty was revealed as the first member of KISS OF LIFE. The group made their official debut on July 5th, 2023, with their self-titled mini album "KISS OF LIFE".
